{"tid":1567381,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【力抗暴政 以善制惡】9.15 香港人行街攻略分析","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T05:46:53.000Z","uid":178013,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"d6fc1658eab3094ccebac62fbc767707b339cf6f","tid":1567381,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家係咪以為羸咗呀?<br />\n唔係嘅話就努力啲宣傳啦!</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n9.15 英領<br />\n時間: 12點<br />\n<br />\n9.15 遊行<br />\n時間: 2點半<br />\n起點: 銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n終點: 遮打道行人專用區<br />\n<br />\n有幾點想講:<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>遊行人數好重要</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n警方俾咗反對通知，如果你身邊朋友猶豫緊出唔出，甚至嗰個係你，請記住香港係有集會自由!但而家已經蕩然無存。<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人必需站出來捍衛香港嘅核心價值。Hong Kong is not China.</span><br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>銀髮族扮演重要角色</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少銀髮族，佢地好關鍵! 警察其實好少搞銀髮族，所以人數多嘅話，佢地可以成為年青人嘅屏障。<br />\n<br />\n3. <ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">勇武和理缺一不可</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n和理非手足請繼續和理非，因為今次遊行人數非常重要，我地要玩到五大訴求應承哂為止，絕對寸步不讓。<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足請繼續帶gear。保護好自己，保護好身邊手足，一個都不能少。隨時要準備同黑警搏鬥，但都要小心。唔好因戀戰而送頭。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武和理團結係運動繼續行落去嘅重要彈藥!</span><br />\n<br />\n4. <ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">嚴防休班警特襲</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n大家都如而家休班警配備警棍，隨時可以毆我地。但係我地絕對唔可以任人魚肉!<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地需要提高警覺，千祈唔好落單。如果真係有手足俾人圍，一定要大嗌求助! 其他人務必救受困手足!</span><br />\n<br />\n5. <ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">退場計劃 (Exit Plan)</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n黨鐵封站係基本動作。<span style=\"color: red;\">要順利退場，我地要變裝!將自己打扮成一個普通市民，隱藏於鬧市當中。</span>大家遊行完可以行街、食飯、睇戲。而家唔係出街都犯法呀嘛?<br />\n總之盡量唔好俾啲狗有理由懷疑你參加集會。<br />\n<br />\n當大家撤緊時，和理非如果聽到有關防暴嘅消息時請保持冷静，唔好拔足狂奔，以免制造恐慌。大家可以急步行，<span style=\"color: red;\">退緊時盡量唔好嗌口號! 太嘈會傳達唔到現場訊息!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"76099d58b3846393844cb7e25c05037e934ad234","tid":1567381,"uid":178013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nLM1zdL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLM1zdL.jpg&h=ec3176b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ipkhR0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipkhR0q.jpg&h=8d3c00e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26d371cd82cf2c2895a0ec0c816da569f58c3021","tid":1567381,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"915 要人"},{"pid":"af5cb7635d5639f5c0add766e4b04dabeb1ce185","tid":1567381,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:12:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d9bc04688fb43a88e71389ea2dbd8f00f5a3f75","tid":1567381,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"6e50f5a43874ee829e19848f5a2b432d2f38a251","tid":1567381,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"未驘架"},{"pid":"8656d1e58ee575716de5e82339fad8a4f3fa3290","tid":1567381,"uid":134450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:14:29.000Z","msg":"推，光復香港"},{"pid":"224f9000be351b1008bff546b08a0c320b8a6d8d","tid":1567381,"uid":200564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e600b264caea88fb5b9d254c16d7bf043dfdc6ef","tid":1567381,"uid":200564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:15:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"6ec2ebd748120cf2ce9c52fe9b2bb38ef3a3fdf1","tid":1567381,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:16:04.000Z"